OL,3,CMan charged with shooting teenage girl
OL,4,Cin the legs
OL,6,FA man has been charged after a teenage
OL,7,Fgirl was shot in the legs.
OL,9,FPolice were called to Lime Grove, off
OL,10,FLodge Lane in Toxteth, on Thursday 12
OL,11,FMarch 2026 after reports that a 17-
OL,12,Fyear-old girl had been injured in a
OL,13,Fshooting inside a house.
OL,15,FAli Karadas has now been charged with
OL,16,Fwounding with intent and possessing a
OL,17,Ffirearm less than 60cm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
