OL,3,CMan charged with shooting teenage girl
OL,4,Cin the legs
OL,6,FThe victim was taken to hospital for
OL,7,Ftreatment and has since been
OL,8,Fdischarged. Police are still appealing
OL,9,Ffor anyone with information to come
OL,10,Fforward.
OL,12,FKaradas, who's 20-years-old, and of
OL,13,FDenman Drive, has been remanded in
OL,14,Fcustody to appear at Wirral Adult
OL,15,FRemand Court on Thursday 16 April.
